Nymphalidae: Hypolimnas octocula marianensis

Extracts from Butterflies of Micronesia ([Nafus and Schreiner 1997](https://www.uog.edu/_resources/files/wptrc/ButterfliesOfMicronesia.pdf.))

GBIF species page

  • GBIF accepted name is Hypolimnas octocula subsp. marianensis Fruhstorfer, 1912
  • 7 occurrences total
  • 7 occurrences from Guam. All are from iNaturalist

Extracts from Butterflies of Micronesia ([Nafus and Schreiner 1997]

GBIF species page
